<HEADLINE>
TEXAS WOMEN AIM TO END LSU STREAK IN NCAA OUTDOOR CHAMPIONSHIPS
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
 
By ANDY FRIEDLANDER 
c.1998 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   In 1986, Texas won the NCAA outdoor championship in women's
track and field.
</P>
<P>
   Since then, there has been only frustration _ and only Louisiana
