   For Release WEDNESDAY AMs, June 3, 1998
</P>
<P>
   A1164 BC-EXP-SHUTTLE-NYT 362 21:53 U A
</P>
<P>
   SHUTTLE BEGINS LAST MISSION TO OUTPOST OF RUSSIANS
</P>
<P>
   A1159 BC-LYNCH-COX 443 21:50 U A
</P>
<P>
   A1152 BC-NY-REPUBS-CONVENE-NYT 636 21:47 U A
