<P>
   KURT-COURTNEY-FILM (Undated) _ Courtney Love has a genius for
alienating people. That's one indisputable fact that emerges in
``Kurt and Courtney,'' the documentary by Nick Bloomfield that
opened on Friday. Ex-boyfriends, ex-employees, acquaintances and
even Ms. Love's father are more than happy to say nasty things
about her. By Jon Pareles. (Moved). &UR;
