to sell out. But shareholders of Monsanto Co. were offered a mere
19 cents a share over the company's stock price of $55.375 earlier
this week to fall into the arms of American Home Products, another
pharmaceutical company. While another bidder may emerge, and a
shareholder lawsuit was filed Wednesday seeking to block the deal,
investors seem likely to go along. By Reed Abelson.
