<TEXT>
<P>
   Abigail Adams National Bancorp, Washington, the holding company
for Adams National Bank, named Jeanne Delany Hubbard chief
executive and chairwoman of the bank after the ouster of Barbara
Davis Blum. The bank is one of the few U.S. banks owned and run by
women.
