textile and apparel business and operate as two separate public
companies. Dixie said Daniel Frierson, its current chairman,
president and chief executive, would be chairman of both companies.
William Fry IV will become president and chief executive of the
floor-covering company, while George Smith will be president and
chief executive of the textile and apparel company. &QL;
